    },
    {
      "height": 620,
      "id": "7362f1430cf3a3bc",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "made one puzzle showing the basic point of the tablet. I can't think of any more wrinkles that the tablet allows.\n- switch back and forth\n- activate through wall (approach chandroid to deal with range)\n\t- bring player through to extend range\n\t\t- slow moving lift (speed challenge for chandroid)\n\n",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 460,
      "x": -6000,
      "y": -5465
    },
    {
      "height": 543,
      "id": "50783dc193c7975f",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Long range tablet (massive distance between player and companion):\n- puzzle solved with dogs that becomes an obstacle course for chandroid?\n- \n\nNew mechanics:\n- colored buttons (red button opens all red doors, etc)\n- chandroid-only puzzle\n\n\n- ",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 480,
      "x": -6570,
      "y": -5405
    },
